</svg></div></div><nav class="diensten_dropdown-content w-dropdown-list"><p class="paragraph-dropdown">Het grootste zoekplatform, Google, heeft veel mogelijkheden waarmee je resultaat kunt behalen. Wees zichtbaar op de zoektermen die er voor jouw bedrijf toe doen en behaal resultaat met de performance gedreven strategie van TNG Agency</p><div class="button-wrapper bottom-marging"><a data-w-id="3de89b47-c782-05e9-21fb-f67f7efbeb91" href="#" class="button is-primary w-inline-block"><div class="text-flip-over-wrapper"><div class="button-text is-primary">Neem contact op</div><div class="button-text is-primary absolute">Neem contact op</div></div></a><a href="/over-ons" class="button is-secondary hide w-inline-block"><div class="text-flip-over-wrapper"><div class="button-text is-secondary">Lees meer</div><div class="button-text is-secondary absolute">Lees meer</div></div></a></div></nav></div><div class="grey-line-2"><div class="black-line"></div></div><div data-hover="false" data-delay="500" data-w-id="5be47f39-0dfe-9f24-fd5f-f09eb85e540e" class="diensten_dropdown w-dropdown"><div class="diensten_dropdown-button w-dropdown-toggle"><div class="diensten-text-move-horizontal"><div class="text-flip-over-wrapper"><div class="diensten_dropdown-title">Microsoft Advertising</div><div class="diensten_dropdown-title absolute">Microsoft advertising</div></div></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="arrow_articles w-embed"><svg height="100%" viewBox="0 0 29 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
